Class ChronicleReaderStream<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • reactor.rx.Stream<MapStream.Signal<K,V>>

        • reactor.rx.stream.io.ChronicleReaderStream<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Map<K,V>, org.reactivestreams.Publisher<MapStream.Signal<K,V>>, NonBlocking
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ChronicleStream

    public class ChronicleReaderStream<K,V>
extends MapStream<K,V>
    Implementation of a Dispatcher that uses a IndexedChronicle to queue tasks to execute.

    Original design on https://github.com/peter-lawrey/Java-Chronicle (MapWrapper and Datastore)

    Author:
    Stephane Maldini
